    "details": {
      "biography": {
        "value": "<p>Oath-broken draugr are the restless dead of warriors who made binding oaths — to clan, to king, to the old powers — and died before fulfilling them. The shame of that failure, magnified by the Rot, has warped them into bitter, powerful undead haunted by their broken word. They fight with the skill and fury of their living selves, but their strikes carry a curse that lingers in wounds and saps the strength of those who survive. They are more dangerous than common draugr and far more driven.</p>",
        "public": ""
      },
